<subSubSection id="DBE740E3E1734FBAF2B517C519C37CC9" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="C4CD541367F2F0C6E356F05C82E666B8" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="94982FED2592D20751D12F0A145E3177" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Characterized by wooly appearance and yellow to orange discs, and distinguished from similar species 
<taxonomicName id="04CF0AADE2191169ACB7E488F1F3E386" class="Ascomycetes" family="Discomycetes" genus="Lachnum" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Lachnum novoguineense subsp. var. var. yunnanicum" order="Helotiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="variety" species="novoguineense" subSpecies="var." variety="yunnanicum">Lachnum novoguineense var. yunnanicum</taxonomicName>
in having shorter ascospores.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
